_sText: zm_complication_v6 Version 6: The Final Version (In the foreseeable future, unless I make a v6a with extra spawn points, but that would only be if requested.) - Approx. 2x the size of v4a - Many more secret rooms - More Hiding Spots - More connecting halls and stairs. - Added an Elevator - Added a Teleport The map has been tested and does not crash servers. Anyone wishing to play on the map before downloading it should either contact me by xfire at natalyaaf to set something up, or to simply go to this server, where the map is in rotation: N/U's Zombie Mod Server 74.86.102.230:27015 Important: Some people on said server reported that a lot of textures are missing. Now, the textures are paked into the map, but if for some reason you don't get all the custom textures, I've created this pack of textures used in the map. That's about it... Feel free to leave any questions or comments!! Natalya[AF]
